    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName ref="#people/151" key="#Commutatio">Adaldo</persName> filio
                            <persName ref="#people/3302">bone memorie Fraiperti</persName> permuta
                        beni con <persName ref="#people/214" key="#Bishops">Gherardus</persName>
                        gratia Dei huius Sancte Lucane ecclesie humilis <rs key="#Bishops"
                            >episcopus</rs>. Adaldo cede a Gherardo ad parte <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/132" key="#Churches">Sancti
                            Silvestri</orgName>, qui est de suppotestatem ipsius episcopatui vestro
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>, et ipse ecclesie Sancti Silvestri esse videtur
                            <placeName ref="#places/4" key="#Cities #Clusae/gates #Walls">foras <rs
                                key="#Walls">muros</rs> huius <rs key="#Cities">civitatis</rs>
                            Lucenses, prope <rs key="#Clusae/gates">porta</rs> Sancti
                            Petri</placeName>, id est duo petie de vinea et terra mea illa, quam
                        abeo in loco <placeName ref="#places/555" key="#Confinia"
                            >Interaccule</placeName>, qui una ex ipse petia de vinea est <rs
                            key="#Confinia">tenentes uno caput cum uno lato</rs> in vinea et terra
                        ipsius episcopatui vestri Sancti Martini, alio caput tenet in <rs>via
                            publica</rs>, alio lato tenet in terra <persName key="#Confinia"
                                ><name>Firmitei</name></persName> (…); quidem et illa alia petia de
                        terra et vinea mea illa in ipso loco <placeName ref="#places/555"
                            key="#Confinia">Interaccule</placeName>, quod est insimul comprehensa,
                        tenentes uno caput in <rs>via publica</rs>, alio caput tenet in terra
                                <persName><name>Adalberti</name></persName>, lato uno tenet &lt;in>
                        terra ipsius episcopatui vestro Sancti Martini et alio lato tenet in terra,
                        qui fuit <persName>quondam <name>Eritei</name></persName> (…); simili modo
                        terra mea illa que esse videtur in loco prope <placeName ref="#places/395"
                            key="#Confinia">Rocta</placeName>, que ipsa <placeName ref="#places/395"
                            >terra vocitatur de Huscunda</placeName>, que est tenentes uno caput in
                        terra ipsius <persName key="#Confinia"><name>Firmitei</name></persName>,
                        alio caput cum uno lato tenet in terra de filii <persName>quondam
                                <name>Ildi</name></persName>, et alio lato tenet in <rs>via
                            publica</rs>; hec predictas petias de vinea et terras (…) quod sunt per
                        mensura ad iusta pertica mensurata <rs key="#Size">modiorum sex et
                            sistariorum tridecim</rs> (…). Riceve in cambio da parte ipsius ecclesie
                        Sancti Silvestri, id est terra illa ubi dicitur <placeName ref="#places/61"
                            >Secturia</placeName>, prope <placeName ref="#places/587">Vico
                            Elingo</placeName>, quas ipsa petia de terra est tenentes uno caput in
                            <rs key="#Rivers">rivo</rs>, alio caput in terra quas quondam Leo ad
                        manus suas abuit et aliquantulo in terra mea q.s. Adaldo, lato uno tenet in
                        via publica, alio lato tenet in terra qui fuit <persName>quondam <name
                                ref="Warnefredus">Vuarnifridi</name></persName> et in terra mea q.s.
                        Adaldo (…); simul et alia petiola de terra et vinea, quod est insimul
                        comprehensa, tenentes uno caput in suprascripto rivo, alio caput tenet in
                        terra, quas suprascripto quondam Leo ad manus suas abuit, lato uno tenet in
                        iam dicta terra mea q.s. Adaldo et ipsius Vuarnifridi, alio lato tenet in
                        terra et vinea, quem suprascripto quondam Leo ad manus abuit (…); quidem et
                        (…) terra illa ubi vocitatur <placeName ref="#places/699">ad
                            Grippo</placeName>, infra loco <placeName ref="#places/587">Vico
                            Elingo</placeName>, qui ipse terra est tenente uno caput in predicto
                        rivo, alio caput tenet in vinea, qui fuit <persName>quondam <name>Lei de
                                    <placeName>Silice</placeName></name></persName>, lato uno tenet
                        in vinea ipsius episcopatui vestro Sancti Martini, alio lato tenet in terra
                        mea q.s. Adaldo (…); hec predictas petia de terra et vinea (…) sunt per
                        mensura ad insta perticha mensurata modiorum tres et sistariorum undecim
                        (…). Ubi et super hanc comutationem tu qui supra <persName ref="#people/214"
                            key="#Bishops">Gherardus</persName> episcopus direxisti <rs
                            key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities">missos tuos</rs> de tua parte,
                        id est <persName><name ref="Andreas">Andrea</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Teudiprandus</name></persName> not seu <persName
                            key="#Witness #Missus_of_other_public_authorities #Other_clerics"
                                ><name>Albolfo</name> clerico</persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Huuarnari">Vuarneri</name></persName> filio
                            <persName>suprascript <name ref="Warnefredus"
                            >Vuarnifridi</name></persName>; et <persName ref="#people/137"
                            key="#Marquis/duke #Missus_of_other_public_authorities"
                            >Adalbertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">dux</rs> de sua partem direxit <rs
                            key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities">missos suos</rs> id est
                            <persName key="#Witness #Notary #Scabini"><name ref="Giselfredus"
                                >Ghiselfridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary #Scabini">notarius et schabino</rs> seu <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Allo">Aloni</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name>Fraimundo</name></persName> germani et filii
                            <persName>quondam <name>Anghalperti</name></persName>, qui super hanc
                        comutationem ambulaverunt hac previderunt et renuntiaverunt quod meliorata
                        comutationem dedisse ad parte suprascripte ecclesie Sancti Silvestri kwam
                        recepisset ut magis omni tempore sint stabile (…). Pena in duplum. <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Ragifunsus"
                            >Rachifonsus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs key="#Commutatio"
                            >cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName ref="#places/4"
                            key="#Mother_churches #Bishops">Luca</placeName>.</ab>
                    <ab>Oltre ai missi inviati dal vescovo e dal duca/marchese di Tuscia,
                        sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Teudemundus">Teudimundus</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name>Baldibertus</name></persName>, Adalpertus
                        notarius, <persName key="#Witness"><name>Uuillerado</name></persName>,
                        Lambertus, <persName key="#Witness #Notary #Scabini"
                            ><name>Roffridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary #Scabini">notarius et schabinus</rs>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name>Himalfridi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Missus_of_other_public_authorities #Other_clerics"><name
                                ref="Leo">Leo</name>
                            <rs key="#Other_clerics">clerico</rs></persName>.</ab>
                </div>
